  <Descripcion>This loft was fixed as a work-place that Charles started using as a chemistry lab, but ended up being used also as a bedroom. Everything is messy and looks like abandoned time ago. There is a strange smell inside you are not able to identify. It's dark since windows have been covered with planks of wood, although some of them have been removed from one window, and there's some light coming into the room. Some candles spread around the room light the scene.
</Descripcion>
