    <ObjetoBase>
      <Nombre>CirculoInvocacion</Nombre>
      <DescripcionNombre>Summoning Circle</DescripcionNombre>
      <ObjetoOpciones>
        <opcionObjeto>Coger</opcionObjeto>
        <opcionObjeto>Observar</opcionObjeto>
      </ObjetoOpciones>
      <TiradasObjeto>
        <ObjetoTiradaBase>
          <TextoDescriptivo>This is some kind of summoning symbol engraved on the wood with a knife, it's full of strange symbols you can't get to identify, there are traces of soil among the whole circle and also a strange black powder you don't identify.</TextoDescriptivo>
          <HabilidadTirada>Ninguna</HabilidadTirada>
          <Comprobacion>false</Comprobacion>
          <EscenaComprobacion>ninguna</EscenaComprobacion>
          <ObjetoComprobacion>Ninguno</ObjetoComprobacion>
          <Accion>false</Accion>
          <LocalizacionAccion />
        </ObjetoTiradaBase>
        <ObjetoTiradaBase>
          <TextoDescriptivo>This is Ibn Ghazi Powder!, this blasphemous powder is used to discern summoned spirits, and it's blent with ashes and soil. </TextoDescriptivo>
          <HabilidadTirada>MitosDeCthulhu</HabilidadTirada>
          <Comprobacion>false</Comprobacion>
          <EscenaComprobacion>ninguna</EscenaComprobacion>
          <ObjetoComprobacion>Ninguno</ObjetoComprobacion>
          <Accion>false</Accion>
          <LocalizacionAccion />
        </ObjetoTiradaBase>
        <ObjetoTiradaBase>
          <TextoDescriptivo>There's a mixture of ashes and soil. The strange powder shows hipnotic shines, which you would never consider as normal in this world. You never saw something like this before, and don't think they belong to an element known on Earth.</TextoDescriptivo>
