          <TextoDescriptivo>You clearly recognize traces of Ibn Ghazi disgusting powder, used on blasphemous rituals in order to discern summoned spirits. For the size of traces, it's been used on large amounts, which makes you imagine how horrible was what happened within these four walls...</TextoDescriptivo>
