      <TiradasObjeto>
        <ObjetoTiradaBase>
          <TextoDescriptivo>A bunch of sheets of paper are hanging along the planks next to the window, and some parts of the wall, there are sheets written in several languages, you get to identify Latin, French and English. Some are graphics about alembics and chemistry accessories.</TextoDescriptivo>
