          <TextoDescriptivo>Pages written in Latin deal about how to set and organize a working table in order to make alchemical experiments. Because of their appearance, used to belong to a very old book.</TextoDescriptivo>
          <HabilidadTirada>OtraLenguaLatin</HabilidadTirada>
